It may have been the first year back after 20 years… but @mxstore’s THUMPERNATS absolutely cemented itself as a stand-out on our 2025 calendar! 🙌🏼

 The grass-track comeback delivered a full weekend of unreal racing, with riders from every corner of the moto world lining up on the gate. Ex-pros, weekend warriors, OG Thumpernats racers, and the next-gen all ready to send it.

 We scored the best seat in the house right along the start straight, the perfect spot as crowds flooded through the tent all weekend. It gave us the prime opportunity to talk all things ODI, surrounded by the sound of motos on full noise.

 Bring on 2026… Thumpernats can’t come quick enough! 🔥🏁

 @odigrips 
