KTM @dm31_racing team has wrapped up a monumental year as they ticked off the final rounds of the 2025 @ausenduro Championship in Gympie, and what a way to finish! 🏁

 It was an all-out domination from the crew, with @milner_31 , @korey_mcmahon153 , and @jontereynders714 each taking home the championship title for their class and stamping their mark on Aussie off-road racing history books.

 Milner also made history, becoming Australia’s most successful domestic off-road racer after locking in his 6th outright ProEnduro crown, a true legend moment! 👏🏻

 We’re incredibly proud to stand behind the team for another year, supporting them every step of the way with ODI Bars and Grips, Albek Hydration packs, Gearbags and Luggage, and of course Australian-made FunnelWeb Air Filters.

