 The CFP program aims to bridge the gap between amateur and professional BMX racing by providing financial support and mentorship to young, promising riders. 

 The program offers cash bonuses for podium finishes in UCI events, encouraging riders to compete at the highest level.

 ODI Grips are proud to be partners to provide resources and support for the program.

