The 2020 Mini Major by @sevenmx is only three weeks away! Now in its fifth year, it has rapidly become the most anticipated event of the year for mini racers. Designed around kids, the Mini Major is a premier race without the premier costs. For $110 kids can race three classes, and there is no membership required, and transponder rentals are free of charge. All in all, the Mini Major is a fun-filled four days with lots to do off the track, too: from a jam-packed vendors’ row to after-hours entertainment like @odigrips BMX night and @ridestacyc races, this is an event not to be missed. And thanks to @KTMUSA and @HusqvarnaMotorcyclesUSA, 45 lucky kids will get to experience an almost-silent moto in the Electric Challenge, a free demo race on KTM E5 and Husqvarna EE 5 electric minis! Pre-registration is filling up fast, so get your kids signed up today at swapmotoraceseries.com 

